title: VERSION
brief: A text-string containing the Lumail version number.
seealso: get_variables, debug
version: 0.08
----

<p>The global variable <span class="tt">VERSION</span> contains the version number of the Lumail release.</p>
<p>For example:</p>
<pre>
msg( "Lumail version: " .. VERSION .. " running on " .. _VERSION );
</pre>
<p><b>NOTE</b>: <span class="tt">_VERSION</a> will return a string such as <span class="tt">Lua 5.1</span>.</p>